From Ed Stastny Subject Chaos Editions IDEA Internation Directory of Electronic Arts I've borrowed the version of this book from a moley What a wealth of Five hundred pages of information about electronic artists and organizations around the globe many have email addresses An up to the minute database of this information is also available on Minitel the book's based in there any Internet Minitel gates The book is printed in French and To have you or your organization listed in IDEA just send your information to Annick Bureaud IDEA rue Falguiere Paris France It's free to be listed in it I'm not sure how widely distributed the book is or how much it I'm not affiliated with them in any way I was just impressed by their collection of organizations and I highly encourage all involved in electronic media video music graphics animation to send in your entry and encourage them to make their database available on Ed Stastny OTIS Project END PROCESS SOUND News and Arts PO BX FTP pub multimedia pictures OTIS Omaha NE projects otis EMail